<lb ed="X" n="0351b14"/><lb ed="R128" n="0701a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第九恒順眾生</cb:mulu><head>第九恒順眾生</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0351b15"/><lb ed="R128" n="0701a04"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351b1501">復次善男子言恒順眾生者<note place="inline">至</note>身語意業無有疲厭。</p>
