<lb ed="X" n="0351b17"/><lb ed="R128" n="0701a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十普皆迴向</cb:mulu><head>第十普皆迴向</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0351b18"/><lb ed="R128" n="0701a07"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351b1801">復次善男子言普皆迴向者<note place="inline">至</note>身語意業無有疲厭。</p>
