<lb ed="X" n="0352c01"/><lb ed="R128" n="0703a14"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0352c0101"><l>處世界如虗空</l><l>似蓮華不著水</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0352c02"/><lb ed="R128" n="0703a15"/><l>心清淨超於彼</l><l>稽首禮無上尊</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0352c03"/><lb ed="R128" n="0703a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">旋遶念誦</cb:mulu><head>旋遶念誦</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0352c04"/><lb ed="R128" n="0703a17"/><list><item xml:id="itemX74p0352c0401">南無法界十方佛</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0352c0408">南無法界十方法</item>
